---
import Terminal from "./ui/Terminal.astro";
import Badge from "./ui/Badge.astro";
---

<section class="py-24 bg-bg-elevated">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Agent-native</p>
      <h2 class="mb-4">Your agent already knows how to use it.</h2>
      <p class="body-lg max-w-[640px] mx-auto mb-4 text-text-secondary">
        Ask your agent what to focus on today. It runs <code
          class="font-mono text-sm bg-bg-surface px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-text-primary"
          >oru context</code
        >, reads the JSON, and tells you Monday is your only free day to file
        taxes before Thursday's deadline. Every command is non-interactive
        — no prompts, no confirmations, deterministic exit codes. Agents
        do not need a browser, an API token, or special handling.
      </p>
      <p class="body max-w-[640px] mx-auto text-text-tertiary">
        Human-readable tables when you run it. Machine-readable JSON when
        your agent does. Same commands, same behavior — no interactive mode
        to work around.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16 max-md:grid-cols-1 reveal"
      data-delay="80"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 min-w-0">
        <div class="text-center">
          <Badge>Human-friendly</Badge>
        </div>
        <Terminal title="oru list">
          <span class="line"><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span> <span class="sub">list</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">     ID        TITLE                     PRI     OWNER  DUE         LABELS  META</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">[ ]  zj9rESjT  </span><span class="cmd">Refactor auth middleware</span><span class="output">  </span><span class="val">high  </span><span class="output">         2026-02-20</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="val">[~]</span><span class="output">  fj6EmFhu  </span><span class="cmd">Write migration tests</span><span class="output">     medium</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">[ ]  yX9K9UbF  </span><span class="cmd">Update API docs</span><span class="output">           low</span></span>
        </Terminal>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 min-w-0">
        <div class="text-center">
          <Badge>Agent-friendly</Badge>
        </div>
        <Terminal title="oru list --json">
          <span class="line"><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span> <span class="sub">list</span> <span class="flag">--json</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">[</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">  {"{"}</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">    </span><span class="key">"id"</span><span class="output">: </span><span class="str">"zj9rESjT-7b1a-..."</span><span class="output">,</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">    </span><span class="key">"title"</span><span class="output">: </span><span class="str">"Refactor auth..."</span><span class="output">,</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">    </span><span class="key">"status"</span><span class="output">: </span><span class="str">"todo"</span><span class="output">,</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">    </span><span class="key">"priority"</span><span class="output">: </span><span class="str">"high"</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">  {"}"}</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">]</span></span>
        </Terminal>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-md:grid-cols-1">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 min-w-0 reveal" data-delay="80">
        <h3 class="">Agents retry. oru handles it.</h3>
        <p class="body text-text-secondary">
          The <code
            class="font-mono text-[13px] bg-bg-surface px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-text-primary"
            >--id</code
          > flag makes creates idempotent — your agent can safely retry without
          creating duplicate tasks.
        </p>
        <Terminal title="idempotent creates">
          <span class="line"><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span> <span class="sub">add</span> <span class="str">"Deploy to staging"</span> <span class="flag">--id</span> <span class="val">019414a3-...</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">019414a3  </span><span class="cmd">Deploy to staging</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">  Status: todo  Priority: medium</span></span>
          <span class="blank"></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span> <span class="sub">add</span> <span class="str">"Deploy to staging"</span> <span class="flag">--id</span> <span class="val">019414a3-...</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">019414a3  </span><span class="cmd">Deploy to staging</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">  Status: todo  Priority: medium</span></span>
        </Terminal>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 min-w-0 reveal" data-delay="160">
        <h3 class="">Key-value metadata on any task.</h3>
        <p class="body text-text-secondary">
          Link tasks to PRs, projects, sprints, or anything else. The <code
            class="font-mono text-[13px] bg-bg-surface px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-text-primary"
            >--meta</code
          > flag takes arbitrary key-value pairs — useful for your own organization
          and for agents to track provenance.
        </p>
        <Terminal title="metadata">
          <span class="line"><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span> <span class="sub">add</span> <span class="str">"Review PR feedback"</span> \</span>
          <span class="line">    <span class="flag">--meta</span> <span class="val">agent=claude-code</span> \</span>
          <span class="line">    <span class="flag">--meta</span> <span class="val">pr=142</span> \</span>
          <span class="line">    <span class="flag">--meta</span> <span class="val">run=a1b2c3</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">019414a4  </span><span class="cmd">Review PR feedback</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">  Status: todo  Priority: medium</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">  Metadata:</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">    agent: claude-code</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">    pr: 142</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">    run: a1b2c3</span></span>
        </Terminal>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
